The format of questionnaire format should be as follows:

# Start of the doc (not required)

---
question: 1        # show order of the question  
type: QA|SC|MC     # type of question, QA:q&a, SC:single choice, MC:multiple choice
[size: S|M|L]      # answer box size S(mall)|M(iddle)|L(arge), for SC and MC, use this to show an 'Other Box'
[stat: false]	   # if this question should be included in statistics
content: content
[options:
  - option content 1
  [- option content 2]
  [- ...]]

---
question: 2
... 

# End of the doc (not required)